entry.def: If someone is swanking, they are speaking about things they own or things they have achieved, in order to impress other people.

example.ex: I have always been against swanking about all the things I have been lucky enough to win.
example.tran: 我一向不喜欢和别人炫耀自己因为幸运而取得的那些成就。

entry.def: Swank means the same as swanky .

example.ex: ...a swank new shop on the outskirts of Beijing.
example.tran: 北京郊区新开的一家高档时尚商店
